              "<strong>Hallamos los puntos de intersección entre f(x) y g(x).</strong>",
              "<strong>Igualamos f(x)=g(x):</strong>",
              "$$x^2-3x+1=2x-3$$",
              "$$x^2-5x+4=0$$",
              "<strong>Utilizamos la resolvente para encontrar las raíces</strong>:",
              "<strong>Entonces:</strong>",
              "$$x=1 \\quad \\quad \\text{y} \\quad \\quad x=4$$",
          
              "<strong>Determinamos quien es techo y piso en el intervalo [1,4].</strong>",
              "<strong>Seleccionamos un valor del intervalo, por ejemplo x=2</strong>",
              "$$f(2)=4-6+1=-1$$",
              "$$g(2)=4-3=1$$",
              "<strong>Entonces g(x) > f(x) en el intervalo, eso significa que g(x) es el techo y f(x) es el piso</strong>",
          
              "<strong>Planteamos el área entre curvas.</strong>",
              "$$A=\\int_{1}^{4} [g(x)-f(x)] dx$$",
              "$$A=\\int_{1}^{4} \\left[(2x-3)-(x^2-3x+1)\\right] dx$$",
          
              "<strong>Simplificamos el integrando:</strong>",
              "$$A=\\int_{1}^{4} (-x^2+5x-4) dx$$",
          
              "<strong>Integramos.</strong>",
              "$$A=\\int (-x^2+5x-4)dx=-\\frac{x^3}{3}+\\frac{5x^2}{2}-4x$$",
          
              "<strong>Aplicamos la regla de Barrow.</strong>",
              "<strong>En x=4:</strong>",
              "$$-\\frac{64}{3}+\\frac{80}{2}-16$$",
              "$$=-\\frac{64}{3}+40-16$$",
              "$$=-\\frac{64}{3}+24$$",
              "$$=\\frac{8}{3}$$",
          
              "<strong>En x=1:</strong>",
              "$$-\\frac{1}{3}+\\frac{5}{2}-4$$",
              "$$=-\\frac{1}{3}+\\frac{5}{2}-\\frac{12}{3}$$",
              "$$=-\\frac{13}{3}+\\frac{5}{2}$$",
              "$$=-\\frac{26}{6}+\\frac{15}{6}$$",
              "$$=-\\frac{11}{6}$$",
          
              "<strong>Restamos:</strong>",
              "$$A=\\frac{8}{3}-(-\\frac{11}{6})$$",
              "$$A=\\frac{16}{6}+\\frac{11}{6}$$",
              "$$A=\\frac{27}{6}$$",
              "$$A=\\frac{9}{2}$$",
          
              "<strong>CONCLUSIÓN:</strong>",
              "El área encerrada entre las curvas es:",
              "$$A=\\frac{9}{2}$$"
        ]
