                    "<strong>Techo: g(x)</strong>",
                    "<strong>Piso: f(x)</strong>",
                
                    "<strong>Planteamos el área entre las curvas.</strong>",
                    "$$A=\\int_{5}^{7} [g(x)-f(x)] dx$$",
                    "$$A=\\int_{5}^{7} \\left[2(x-5)-(x-5)^2\\right] dx$$",
                    "$$A=\\int_{5}{7} \\left[2x-10-x^2+10x-25\\right]dx$$",
                
